  "texts": [
    "The transformer model is trained on the oversampled data with extreme values.",
    "The total of encoder and decoder layers in the Transformer model is 2 which is the most common as more layers can capture more complex patterns but increase computational cost.",
    "Attention heads are set to 2 which is specifically used to focus on different parts of patterns as this paper hypothesizes two distributions (distribution of normal values and distribution of extreme values) head are set to capture both of them.",
    "As the forecasting horizon is 72 for all models, the output size is 72.",
    "The learning rate for the Adam [42] optimized is scheduled to change 1 % with an initial value of 0.001."
  ],
